{"tid":2067983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本港今日17/6暴增8宗中國肺炎確診個案！","createTime":"2020-06-17T10:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T11:26:08.000Z","uid":63113,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1af930ec2d0a126e664cfa9c444ab0d7070bc4fa","tid":2067983,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T10:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057839161bd1e67fee27efecd395caab355ba940","tid":2067983,"uid":63113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9bkLtJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9bkLtJ.gif&h=23f32629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=16898&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fott-news.i-cable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D16898%26ct%3D1&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=33d48a78\" target=\"_blank\">https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=16898&amp;ct=1</a>"},{"pid":"346e6abcc3f8aba2cea786b6ccd515f143d03487","tid":2067983,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"有無本地"},{"pid":"f5a01e6b252a9f1425489ab02f8bac2cacd1951e","tid":2067983,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T10:58:05.000Z","msg":"RTHK：新增確診患者分別為2男6女，年齡介乎4至70歲，潛伏期分別身處菲律賓或巴基斯坦"},{"pid":"71cb9e0a3ac48eef4d6bb91a9d5d883cdca0999b","tid":2067983,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"本港新增8宗外地輸入新型肺炎確診病例 <br />\n2020-06-17 HKT 18:56<br />\n<br />\n本港新增8宗新型冠狀肺炎確診個案，全屬外地輸入，確診個案累計1120宗，另外1宗疑似個案。<br />\n  <br />\n新增確診患者分別為2男6女，年齡介乎4至70歲，潛伏期分別身處菲律賓或巴基斯坦，當中只有1名7歲男童曾經出發燒及流鼻水的病徵，其他患者都無病徵。衞生防護中心正繼續跟進確診個案的流行病學調查，及接觸者追蹤的工作。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局表示，再多2名新型肺炎確診患者出院，至今共有1071人已出院，留院的38人中，3人危殆，1人嚴重，其餘情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n另外，截至下午4時，衞生防護中心已經在祿泉樓收回及檢測1066個第二輪的深喉唾液樣本，全部對新型冠狀病毒呈陰性反應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532641-20200617.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532641-20200617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=1d052cc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532641-20200617.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=da6bbc7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532641-20200617.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d671986bc464a881502a8e7f9b3a72d0675470f2","tid":2067983,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚咪煩啦"},{"pid":"51275c72d96dbb06ca0a0a29be00a8f7d956b8be","tid":2067983,"uid":89683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:05:30.000Z","msg":"輸入唔計<br />\n本土個案可追查唔計<br />\n<br />\n但永續限聚令"},{"pid":"29cc932351b02d8a6776eedf51de44e36064bf36","tid":2067983,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nw9dfer.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNw9dfer.gif&h=3c3c2223&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fg5Px07.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffg5Px07.gif&h=8b60eee3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48ccb6b29867803875e5468594ecfb40fa4bcd6d","tid":2067983,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:14:47.000Z","msg":"醫管局表示，再多2名新型肺炎確診患者出院，至今共有1071人已出院，留院的38人中，3人危殆，1人嚴重，其餘情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n都半年喇<br />\n咩跳唔到10cm嗰啲全部都係嚟自中國啲9upper<br />\n個病毒係堅定流<br />\n心中有數"},{"pid":"0e9247b8c7fbdf4256658d74857b9eb6625e7d74","tid":2067983,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d671986bc464a881502a8e7f9b3a72d0675470f2","tid":2067983,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚咪煩啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:14:58.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚咪煩啦"},{"pid":"d52a19e43d1dfc6bf962246e1d56638cb13286eb","tid":2067983,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:16:08.000Z","msg":"好的，支那武漢肺炎。"},{"pid":"b9d9e74fb58c416bee651f9573772fa59fe07b4d","tid":2067983,"uid":252993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:23:32.000Z","msg":"只能證明，在菲律賓及巴基斯坦，疫症仍廣泛流行"},{"pid":"9ba24227e38ce4c7da98317442e532f5b0672181","tid":2067983,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:26:08.000Z","msg":"支那啊"}]}